HEADWORD: Receptivity
<hw>Rec`ep*tiv"i*ty</hw> <pr>(r⟦ecr⟧s`⟦ecr⟧p*t⟦icr⟧v"⟦icr⟧*t⟦ycr⟧ ⟦or⟧
